						<p>I guess:<br />
- send a bug report to the extension developer (if it&#8217;s a bug)<br />
- add alert to users using firefox</p>
<p>I don&#8217;t see any other feasible options. I had some users complain that some site wasn&#8217;t working well. They had a banner blocking extension that removed images in certain folders by default. You just can&#8217;t find every one of them and rename all your image folders&#8230;</p>
